<br>
Unfortunately the growth and popularity of the board which in turn has added to immaturity of some of the visitors to the bar has forced the addition of rules to the board. <br>
<br>
Any post that is posted after the date and time of the posted rules will mean that you agree to the these new rules.<br>
<br>
I hope everyone understand why these rules are being added. Let's continue having fun on the board and stop the unnecessary flames.<br>
<br>
Remember you are a guest here, act like one.<br>
<br>
1) If you start a flame thread in any other forum than Rants and Flames, the administrator or moderators will move it to the &quot;right&quot; forum or just delete it. Repeatedly breaking the rules will lead to your being banned.<br>
<br>
2) If you reply with a flame in any other forum than Rants and Flames, the administrator or moderators will delete it. Repeatedly breaking the rules will lead to your being banned.<br>
<br>
3) Don't act like a juvenile dickwad. Repeatedly doing so will get you banned.<br>
<br>
4) Adult material is NOT allowed. Pornographic stories, pictures, violent stories, etc. are NOT allowed. Post them and they will get deleted.  Repeatedly breaking the rules will lead to your being banned.<br>
<br>
